# Icons Usage

- Replace all inline `<svg>` and ASCII emojis with `react-icons`.
- Prefer `react-icons/hi2` (Heroicons v2). Use consistent size/color via Tailwind classes.
- Example: use `HiCalendarDays`, `HiClock`, `HiMapPin` for date/time/location.
- In email templates, avoid SVG/React Icons; use text labels instead for broad client compatibility.
